Requirements
============

On Debian
----------

$ sudo aptitude install cmake libgnome-keyring-dev libgphoto2-2-dev libqt4-dev

On MacOS/X
----------

$ sudo port install cmake qt4-mac

Building wDesktop
=================

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

Note: if you are running MacOS/X and are using Qt from macports, invoke cmake as:

$ cmake .. -DQT_QMAKE_EXECUTABLE=/opt/local/libexec/qt4-mac/bin/qmake

